T = \frac{\sigma^2}{2(n-1)}\sum_{i=1}^{i=n-1}(Y_{i+1}-Y_i)^2 
\implies E[T^2] = \frac{\sigma^4}{4(n-1)^2}\{\sum_{i=1}^{i=n-1}E(Y_{i+1}-Y_i)^4+\sum_j\sum_{i \neq j}E(Y_{i+1}-Y_i)^2 E(Y_{j+1}-Y_j)^2\}
= \frac{\sigma^4}{4(n-1)^2} \{12(n-1)+4(n-1)(n-2)\} = \frac{\sigma^4}{(n-1)} \{n+1\}
\implies Var(T) = \frac{2\sigma^4}{n-1}
